Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.62,0:20:39.63,ED_chi,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(500,500)}融化在海风中的面孔
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.63,0:20:44.51,ED_chi,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(500,500)}现在却已化为泡影
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.55,0:20:52.35,ED_chi,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(500,500)}这回忆鲜明的仿若真实
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.35,0:20:57.27,ED_chi,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(500,500)}一次又一次的在我眼前重现
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:05.32,ED_chi,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(500,500)}即使是虚假的也好
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.16,0:21:10.20,ED_chi,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(500,500)}请更加紧密的跟在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.33,0:21:15.50,ED_chi,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(0,500)}明明马上就要说出喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.50,0:21:18.75,ED_chi,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(500,0)}可是唯有时间在不断流逝
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.46,0:21:24.26,ED_chi,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(500,500)}啊 好想回到过去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.01,0:21:33.39,ED_chi,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\blur0\bord0\fad(500,500)}听了许多失恋的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.52,0:21:41.40,ED_chi,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\blur0\bord0\fad(500,500)}只会在角落哭泣的我
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.48,0:21:43.74,ED_chi,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\blur0\bord0\fad(500,500)}好想舍弃这样的我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.74,0:21:46.70,ED_chi,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\blur0\bord0\fad(500,0)}不要再逞强了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.70,0:21:51.45,ED_chi,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\blur0\bord0\fad(0,500)}坦率的去面对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.37,0:21:58.33,ED_chi,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\blur0\bord0\fad(500,600)}真是 太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.62,0:20:39.63,ED_jpn,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(500,500)}潮風に溶けた面影は
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.63,0:20:44.51,ED_jpn,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(500,500)}幻のままで今も
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.55,0:20:52.35,ED_jpn,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(500,500)}リアルで鮮明な思い出は
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.35,0:20:57.27,ED_jpn,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(500,500)}何度も何度も繰り返す
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:05.32,ED_jpn,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(500,500)}嘘でもいいからそばにいてよ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.16,0:21:10.20,ED_jpn,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(500,500)}もっと近くで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.33,0:21:15.50,ED_jpn,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(0,500)}すぐ好きになって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.50,0:21:18.75,ED_jpn,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(500,0)}時間だけが過ぎて
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.46,0:21:24.26,ED_jpn,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(500,500)}あぁ…戻りたいな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.01,0:21:33.39,ED_jpn,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\blur0\bord0\fad(500,500)}失恋ソング沢山聴いて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.52,0:21:41.40,ED_jpn,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\blur0\bord0\fad(500,500)}泣いてばかりの私はもう
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.48,0:21:43.74,ED_jpn,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\blur0\bord0\fad(500,500)}捨てたいから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.74,0:21:46.70,ED_jpn,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\blur0\bord0\fad(500,0)}強がらないで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.70,0:21:51.45,ED_jpn,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\blur0\bord0\fad(0,500)}素直になってよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.37,0:21:58.33,ED_jpn,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\blur0\bord0\fad(500,600)}なんて遅いよね
